title: A review of Episode 1204 Steve Rinella
description:
Steve Rinella is a world class hunter and one of the best representatives for it. Check out his podcast Meateater to learn more. He is a good friend of Joe's and got him into hunting. Their conversations are always great. Check out his new book on cooking wild meats.
